RELEASE NOTES


	A simple to use Active Directory Export tool.

        Export Active Directory data on Users, Contacts,
	Groups and Computer objects.
	ADBulk Export is amazingly simple to use yet a powerful
	application that allows you to export as much information
	as you require from Active Directory relating to your Users,
	Contacts, Groups and Computer objects.

  * Export Users, Contacts, Computers, Groups, Group Membership
  * Export easily to Excel, CSV format, semi-colon separated or SQL database
  * Ideal for migration when used with AD Bulk Users or AD Bulk Contacts
  * GUI or command line operation
  * Filter the results, search within the results
  * 400% quicker than version 2
  * Supports Active Directory running on Windows 2000, 2003 and 2008 Server
  * All attributes can be exported
  * No server components or agents to install
  * No changes or modifications to Active Directory required

Ideal for Active Directory Migration when used with AD Bulk Users and AD Bulk Contacts. Works with Microsoft Active Directory running on Windows 2000, 2003 and 2008 Server. Microsoft Exchange 2000, 2003 and 2007 attributes can be exported.
